Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.62,0:22:50.38,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever Wherever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.66,0:22:59.64,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新たな旅立ち 迎えよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.93,0:23:10.23,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失いかけていたsoul
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.39,0:23:14.58,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼び覚ましたconfined
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.90,0:23:24.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共にした日々を 強く握りしめ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.99,0:23:29.78,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever Wherever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.04,0:23:33.73,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互いに寄り添い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.05,0:23:38.53,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐れことなどない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.00,0:23:44.33,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇が二人わかずとも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.51,0:23:53.45,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確かなことが　そう告げているから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.83,0:24:03.14,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再びで会えるまで　思いよどうか君と
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.31,0:24:10.34,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.62,0:22:50.38,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时 无论何地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.66,0:22:59.64,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎接新的征程
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.93,0:23:10.23,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因失去而感到痛苦的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.39,0:23:14.58,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这禁闭之地 被唤醒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.90,0:23:24.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧抓住共同度过的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.99,0:23:29.78,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时 无论何地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.04,0:23:33.73,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人相互靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.05,0:23:38.53,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无需惧怕任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.00,0:23:44.33,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使黑暗会让两人分离
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.51,0:23:53.45,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为「正确」这样告诉我 直到再会之时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.83,0:24:03.14,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的思念会一直伴于君侧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.31,0:24:10.34,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.07,0:01:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是为了引出我的母亲 柯蒂丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.61,0:01:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才把我移送到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.43,0:01:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我呼喊请求别人的帮助的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.03,0:01:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我母亲必定会现身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.65,0:01:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人 布洛瓦侯爵就是这样认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:02:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但和他的意愿相反 我一直保持沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底 就算我呼喊 母亲也不一定来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 怎么说她也是你的母亲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.28,0:02:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道你身处困境的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在很小的时候 我仅见过母亲一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你拿着这个 我随时都会来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论你身处何方 我一定会赶来到你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个项坠成为了我和母亲羁绊的唯一证明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我把那个证明…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.76,0:03:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 维多利加…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.84,0:03:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 你就这样来到这里接我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一如既往的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了你 我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H000008&\fs24\pos(424,367)}那个箱子沉睡于螺旋迷宫之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 维多利加 脸上粘着奶油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把这个也一并带过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有进步了啊 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.47,0:03:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢当
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你还是平时一样扯高气扬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东洋少年出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为他可能是来带走幼狼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用理会 就这样由着他们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 目标猎物自己上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到魔术幻灯秀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩·罗斯可先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有招待信 突然造访 真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像您这样高贵的大人能大驾光临 我们感到很荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.33,0:04:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在这场宴会上表演的不是什么魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是真真正正地奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必让我学习 见识一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就尽情享受去咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘了监视他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定会和柯蒂丽亚·盖洛一起行动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗杰那只老鼠…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是什么机器？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是幻灯机吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就是能放映出影片的机器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它可以投影出相片图片之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 这个东西出现在这里就表示…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 一个人在那里点头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.66,0:05:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汉特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这个地方做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 有些小事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:05:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有受伤吧 身穿蕾丝裙的小小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松开你下流的双手 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人叫汉特 是钟表师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.48,0:06:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他在同一部列车上认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便问一下 那是机油吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指甲缝里有些脏东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些是涂有磷的气球 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把工作放在一边没事吗 钟表师？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正回程的列车还没来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 和你一起 似乎可以开开眼界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:07:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支撑身体的器具被隐藏在幕布里面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 那是带有滑轮的发条似的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.97,0:07:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.14,0:07:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手枪里装的子弹是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是用锡和水合成的子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一开枪就会碎掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就让客人用这样的枪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就把早就藏好的真子弹咬在嘴里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.54,0:07:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是欺骗无知群众的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩个真是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这晃悠什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你而言 魔术是你的拿手绝活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是你啊 老先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 你见到你女儿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找不到我女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把她隐藏在哪里了?  死神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想带走我女儿就带走吧 我不会阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:08:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如此一来 你将会背负沉重的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我还要去找同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 请大家注意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是姐姐 卡蜜拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是妹妹 摩瑞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们就是这个村子里非常有名的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有魔力血统的最后幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以说是最后的古老力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命名为 菲尔姐妹的箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你们睁大眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.91,0:08:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细地欣赏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会发生什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交换了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经在这片大陆上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处是古老力量的欧洲血统中充满了魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们对此已经习以为常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在又怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.94,0:09:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧煤炭的列车在奔驰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞艇翱翔天空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.01,0:09:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过电波 我们就能听到远方之人的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这些都是值得雀跃的发展
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面 我们是不是也忘记了重要的力量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 比如 站在那里的你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们重要的力量是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是科学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.97,0:09:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汉特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便奇迹就在眼前发生 你还抱有这种想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.47,0:09:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是诡计
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这哪里算得上奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:09:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也请你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这个箱子里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.59,0:10:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.51,0:10:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用科学绝对无法解释的 古老力量的伟大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身处新时代的无礼年轻人啊 给你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,予以审判
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.57,0:10:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思 那我就来证明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证明这全都只是诡计而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把刀放在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证明绳子没有被动过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要刀没有掉下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.16,0:11:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止他们 不然的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人畏惧的魔力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次展现奇迹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.85,0:11:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩瑞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刚才的那把短剑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他们的手还绑在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.79,0:11:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那会是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快离开帐篷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 不要吸入这个烟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.27,0:12:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个烟里有致幻剂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让观众相信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些在宴会中表演的魔术都是真的 才会如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 烟雾太浓了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里等我 我马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.78,0:12:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面…里面危险的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩 他为什么在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说想要对维多利加做什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又见面了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城一弥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.65,0:13:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蒂莉亚 你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗物箱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵异部也真有两把刷子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们似乎被抢先了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.47,0:13:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁断之箱已经丢失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子 把这个给那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉她 解开谜题 为了活下去展现自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请去见见维多利加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.90,0:13:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直非常想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.46,0:13:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至在我眼前哭泣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经止住烟雾的源头了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是有人对装置动了手脚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和小狼在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 稍微再陪我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吧那群家伙的注意集中到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十多年前 也是你在这里吓唬了德军吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坠落的玛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个事件也是…布莱恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.27,0:14:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时是你 在别西卜的头骨上引发的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 利用那台幻灯机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.86,0:14:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道你当时为什么会出手相助科学部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:14:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我想问的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.68,0:15:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都过了十年 为什么你和母亲会特地来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们和灵异部都拥有一件对方想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼 你考虑过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后将是代表新大陆的科学时代
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.82,0:15:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能得到那份力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不是我们这样古老的种族 也不是灵异部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.58,0:15:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是科学部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了消减他们的力量所需要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是遗物箱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我在大战期间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏在那个幻灯机房间里的禁断的秘密之箱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 一不小心说溜嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 没有的小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.75,0:15:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一件事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩 到底在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在遥远的中世纪的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为害怕黑死病龟缩在这里的当时的国王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被黑色死神拖入了冥界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东洋的黑色死神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.69,0:16:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今晚是为了带走何人而来到这个地方的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我推测到我的妻子柯蒂丽亚会坐那趟列车上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她没有现身而你却出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.05,0:16:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的妻子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.85,0:16:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我打发时间确实不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我搭语时的那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.87,0:17:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你比我想象的更加可疑啊 久城一弥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是 维多列加的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚伯特·德·布洛瓦侯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神啊 多亏了你引发的一连串死亡以及案件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的小灰狼锻炼了头脑 更接近于完成形
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是因我而生的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便在欧洲 她也是唯一有效的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望她更加的趋于完美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侯爵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水闸…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有效的道具？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是为了这种目的才生下维多利加…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那东西是我的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都取决于我的判断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了治理国家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样 你也有爱惜和保护维多利加的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.31,0:18:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血缘的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄毛小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侯爵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要带走维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会把她留在你身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要如此吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那个学院也和这里一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在我的手掌心里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.19,0:18:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不论你们去何方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次到来的大风暴中 任何人都无法安然幸免
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海水从水闸涌进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:18:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,列车在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多列加
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道是吸了刚才的烟雾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.75,0:19:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点 来 站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 是Masquerade号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 这下可得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管我了 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊 我怎么可能这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连自己出生的意义都不知道 怎么可能奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.40,0:19:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 这样一来连你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才遇到你的父亲了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.33,0:19:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些大人都是自说自话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我们可是认真烦恼 认真思考地活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存的意义 等会儿慢慢考虑就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.61,0:20:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回学园吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是为此来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了你找到我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.30,0:20:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了你 我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了你 我才明白爱 得到那温柔的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.59,0:20:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.95,0:20:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.33,0:20:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后也要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加把劲儿 抓住这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别西卜的头骨…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被死亡诅咒的要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍蝇王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 我们还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.34,0:21:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你的功劳 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.86,0:22:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.52,0:22:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是… 难道是妈妈的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.24,0:22:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有她让我捎给你口信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开谜团 为了活下去展示你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.71,0:22:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且她还说了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈依然深爱着娇小的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你不呼喊 我也会像这样在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.07,0:24:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了活下去展示自己的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.21,0:24:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 我一定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.41,0:24:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加 加油 Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.41,0:24:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以给我闭嘴吗
